{{Quote|HAH! Some station master she is. Can't even take care of the pirates in the lower level. Look at the chaos around you, my friend.|[[Tarand Crowe/Legends|Tarand Crowe]], about [[Inaldra/Legends|Inaldra]]|<ref name="SWG:TtI">{{SWGcite|exp=NGE|type=general|Talk to Inaldra|Tansarii Point Station}}</ref>}}
'''Station Master''' was a title given to a commanding officer of a [[Space station/Legends|space station]]. After the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], the station master of [[Tansarii Point Station/Legends|Tansarii Point Station]], in the [[Bright Jewel system/Legends|Bright Jewel system]], was [[Inaldra/Legends|Inaldra]].<ref name="SWG:TtI" />

